07:22.739 --> 07:26.140
I'm 17. I don't think
I have a deal yet.

07:26.142 --> 07:27.325
Ah, come on.

07:27.327 --> 07:28.610
Everybody's got a deal.

07:28.612 --> 07:30.695
Your deal is you got no deal.

07:30.697 --> 07:32.831
Cool.

07:32.833 --> 07:35.250
I'm a man without a deal.

07:35.252 --> 07:38.586
What are you, like, a high
school senior or something?

07:38.588 --> 07:40.872
Well, I should be,
but they got this dumb rule

07:40.874 --> 07:43.041
that you have to pass
every single course.

07:44.427 --> 07:47.011
I think five out of seven
is plenty, don't you?

07:47.013 --> 07:48.463
Heck yeah.

07:48.465 --> 07:51.015
In eighth grade,
I flunked all my courses.

07:51.017 --> 07:51.933
Really?

07:51.935 --> 07:53.051
Yeah.

07:53.053 --> 07:54.436
My mom had me evaluated.

07:54.438 --> 07:55.687
Turns out, I was just bored

07:55.689 --> 07:57.889
'cause I was too smart
for all the classes.

07:59.558 --> 08:01.776
Huh. Maybe that's my problem.

08:04.346 --> 08:06.531
I'm too freakin' smart.

08:07.733 --> 08:08.700
Ow!

08:08.702 --> 08:09.951
I'm sorry.

08:09.953 --> 08:12.487
I just think we need
to establish some boundaries.

08:12.489 --> 08:15.790
Hey, don't make hitting
your deal.

08:17.693 --> 08:19.377
