08:35.095 --> 08:38.062
Yeah, and I also
used to have my own room.

08:38.831 --> 08:40.548
What do you
want, Jake?

08:40.549 --> 08:42.717
Okay, so you know how
you're worried that 'cause I get

08:42.719 --> 08:44.853
bad grades in high school
that I'm not gonna be able

08:44.855 --> 08:47.188
to get into college and then
find a job to support myself?

08:47.190 --> 08:50.525
That pretty much
sums it up, yeah.

08:50.527 --> 08:54.662
Well, it turns out, I get
bad grades 'cause I'm too smart.

08:59.552 --> 09:01.068
Too smart?

09:01.070 --> 09:02.236
Yeah.

09:02.238 --> 09:03.404
So I'm gonna forget college,

09:03.406 --> 09:05.673
drop out of high school
and start my own business.

09:05.675 --> 09:08.793
Hold on, hold on.

09:08.795 --> 09:10.845
You're too smart?

09:10.847 --> 09:13.014
Yep. Walden and me
have that in common.

09:13.016 --> 09:16.518
