have that in common.

09:16.520 --> 09:20.605
No offense, Dad, but I don't
think you're that smart.

09:22.391 --> 09:25.944
So, you're saying you want
to drop out of high school?

09:25.946 --> 09:26.978
Why not?

09:26.980 --> 09:28.396
Did you know that Walden made

09:28.398 --> 09:29.931
his first million
before he was 19?

09:29.933 --> 09:32.450
How many zeros
in a million, Jake?

09:32.452 --> 09:35.320
M-I-L-L-I-O-N.

09:37.039 --> 09:38.540
One.

09:41.293 --> 09:44.278
Okay, okay, Jake,
listen carefully.

09:44.280 --> 09:46.414
You are not
dropping out of high school.

09:46.416 --> 09:47.131
But...

09:47.133 --> 09:48.333
No, you're not a genius,

09:48.335 --> 09:50.168
