10:20.269 --> 10:21.601
Come in.

10:21.603 --> 10:22.636
Got a minute?

10:22.638 --> 10:23.970
Sure.

10:23.972 --> 10:27.274
Hey, I'm getting dressed
for my dinner with Bridget.

10:27.276 --> 10:28.525
How do I look?

10:28.527 --> 10:30.977
Your face should be
on gay money.

10:30.979 --> 10:32.829
Listen, um...

10:34.582 --> 10:37.617
You say something to my son
about quitting high school

10:37.619 --> 10:38.818
and starting a business?

10:38.820 --> 10:41.088
Oh, yeah, I told him
that's what I did.

10:41.090 --> 10:44.124
Hey, what do you think
about a hat?

10:44.126 --> 10:45.792
The only reason
to wear a hat on date

10:45.794 --> 10:46.993
is if you're hiding a bald spot.

10:46.995 --> 10:48.428
Oh.

10:50.214 --> 10:51.848
For your next date.

10:54.668 --> 10:56.520
Thank you.

10:56.522 --> 10:58.671
So you really quit high school?

10:58.673 --> 10:59.806
Mmm, no.

10:59.808 --> 11:01.358
I skipped high school.

11:01.360 --> 11:02.609
I quit MIT.

11:02.611 --> 11:04.611
Oh, okay. See, there's
the misunderstanding.

11:04.613 --> 11:07.898
Jake has a hard time
spelling MIT.

11:07.900 --> 11:10.617
Oh. Well, then, he really
shouldn't quit school.

11:10.619 --> 11:12.869
Hey, check it out.

11:12.871 --> 11:14.454
